{"tid":2370359,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳冠希上節目全程冷笑耍大牌？ 何炅強忍怒火：你要尊重我的工作","createTime":"2021-01-18T03:45:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T05:10:56.000Z","uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"045363acec2c06e147256e09e1d8548c3f3389e4","tid":2370359,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T03:45:36.000Z","msg":"陳冠希（Edison）自從淡出娛樂圈後，主力打理自家時裝品牌，並與老婆秦舒培及囡囡Alaia定居美國。不過Edison近年因為在日本街頭鬧爆一名偷拍他的主播，以及與余文樂多次因為自家潮牌隔空對罵而被指脾氣火爆，近日有網民重提當年內地主持人何炅與Edison的一段「恩怨」，但結果反而意想不到？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210116/427185900280090624078146.jpeg/NvF9MPPaujPstXCstBhs-LLGQ5JeRA4yvfijcb34o3E?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210116%2F427185900280090624078146.jpeg%2FNvF9MPPaujPstXCstBhs-LLGQ5JeRA4yvfijcb34o3E%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=01354cd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nEdison當年憑着靚仔外形而爆紅，尤其是他歪嘴而又帶點壞男孩感覺的笑容更是迷倒萬千少女，他在當紅時曾獲邀上由內地著名主持人何炅主持的節目，但在節目中他全程掩嘴笑，態度輕蔑，令何炅大感不快，何炅曾在節目《嚮往的生活》中提及這段往事，認為Edison非常不禮貌：「我說陳先生您是很火，但是其實對我來講，你只是我今天的一個來賓，我尊重你，但我覺得你也要尊重我的工作。我覺得不管怎麼樣，你還是應該認真地聽人家講話，就算我跟你不熟，你一直在那邊笑也是不對的。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210116/427187858726457344401835.jpeg/Ot9Wez2rlMMudk7Z0KfGrAmDUmZcBLDlGn3Lchp9y3I?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210116%2F427187858726457344401835.jpeg%2FOt9Wez2rlMMudk7Z0KfGrAmDUmZcBLDlGn3Lchp9y3I%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=2a9c0dff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過原來Edison並不是耍大牌，而是解釋道：「是因為你今天全程都在叫我陳奕迅。」令何炅非常尷尬，更自嘲他不但叫錯對方的中文名，連英文名都叫成「Eason」。不過亦反映出雖然Edison作風我行我素，但其實脾氣並不是傳言所講的這麼差，而自從囡囡Alaia出世後，他亦收斂了不少，更經常慈父上身，大曬與家人的溫馨合照！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210116/427186073936859136532704.jpeg/iYYSWWY1GB6S9seQRdQNYFd7sy0udhEJJxswxycbMMc?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210116%2F427186073936859136532704.jpeg%2FiYYSWWY1GB6S9seQRdQNYFd7sy0udhEJJxswxycbMMc%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=db7586fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a84233ff93c98a4ceb15635e4c62074785292751","tid":2370359,"uid":389648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T03:59:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f68964a84d1a4693d0c05ee341fad91e91134a","tid":2370359,"uid":61207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T04:00:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d9cfa48110b08219557bf595d2a13b9b1ea17b6","tid":2370359,"uid":198688,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T04:03:18.000Z","msg":"要學杜德偉咁唔理佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20130908/UIW7Z5WYK34WOQ5V6MTS2HWLPU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20130908%2FUIW7Z5WYK34WOQ5V6MTS2HWLPU%2F&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS92UZYMvR53lMa2%2BnKJB5b4%3D&h=cd33cc67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20130908%2FUIW7Z5WYK34WOQ5V6MTS2HWLPU%2F&h=7af07396\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20130908/UIW7Z5WYK34WOQ5V6MTS2HWLPU/</a>"},{"pid":"18d6b40df1f7897717db4f9031343171750b411b","tid":2370359,"uid":84409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T04:05:13.000Z","msg":"有冇當年既片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a596b721fae97cbb0be7b604b63ed115980da3d","tid":2370359,"uid":58630,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T04:06:07.000Z","msg":"叫人上你節目仲講錯人個名 有冇咁兒戲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji